title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Mar 1 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Mar 1 2022
description:
The Ukraine situation looks like it's getting worse, and Buck warned during the show, "It's not gonna be quick. It's not gonna be a limited conflict in terms of duration, I think." Cuomo attempts the comeback Clay predicted. Clay and Buck discuss TV shows. Harris and Pelosi go off script. CBS highlights plight of transgenders in Ukraine. Dr. Leana Wen's flip-flops on everything.
